statements: SELECT * FROM customer_feedback_response_times;
SELECT feedback_id, customer_id FROM customer_feedback_response_times WHERE response_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT customer_id, response_time FROM customer_feedback_response_times ORDER BY response_time DESC;
SELECT * FROM customer_feedback_response_times WHERE customer_id = 1001 AND response_time < '2022-05-01';
SELECT feedback_id, customer_id, response_time FROM customer_feedback_response_times WHERE feedback_id = 5001;
SELECT * FROM customer_feedback_response_times ORDER BY response_time DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT customer_id, MAX(response_time) AS latest_response_time FROM customer_feedback_response_times GROUP BY customer_id;
SELECT customer_id, COUNT(feedback_id) AS total_feedbacks FROM customer_feedback_response_times GROUP BY customer_id HAVING COUNT(feedback_id) > 10;
SELECT customer_id, response_time FROM customer_feedback_response_times WHERE customer_id = 100 ORDER BY response_time ASC;

SELECT customer_id, COUNT(feedback_id) AS total_feedbacks, AVG(response_time) AS average_response_time FROM customer_feedback_response_times GROUP BY customer_id ORDER BY total_feedbacks DESC, average_response_time ASC LIMIT 5;
